\item[4.] {\bf Prompting} the LLM in {\em retrieval-augmented mode} using the top-ranked passages. The prompt explicitly includes the book title, S and P. For recall, this is an {\em ensemble} over different choices of retrieved 
 passage (step 1.), 
 and the output of this stage is the union of all objects generated by the LLM.